      <title>特朗普获胜后，债券交易员通过看跌期权押注获利数百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bond-traders-net-millions-on-bearish-option-bets-after-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在国债期权市场，投机者似乎正在利用几周前押注的收益率上升的收益来获利，并可能获得数百万美元的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bond-traders-net-millions-on-bearish-option-bets-after-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦称特朗普当选对全球经济构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-villeroy-says-trump-election-poses-risks-to-global-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，唐纳德·特朗普当选为下一任美国总统将给全球经济带来风险和不确定性，并应鼓励欧洲解决其弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-villeroy-says-trump-election-poses-risks-to-global-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南达科他州将撤销管道法，对美国乙醇造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/south-dakota-is-set-to-pull-pipeline-law-in-blow-for-us-ethanol</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拟建的价值 89 亿美元的碳捕获管道项目曾使美国玉米带出现两极分化，如今在南达科他州又遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/south-dakota-is-set-to-pull-pipeline-law-in-blow-for-us-ethanol</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:26:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“特朗普交易”掌控市场：华尔街反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/-trump-trade-takes-hold-of-markets-wall-street-reacts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市创下历史新高，债券收益率飙升，美元有望创下 2020 年以来的最佳单日表现，投资者正在关注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫以及他的政策对市场的影响。彭博电视台的嘉宾对市场走势发表了看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/-trump-trade-takes-hold-of-markets-wall-street-reacts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:24:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普有办法在第二任期内解雇强大的金融监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗希特·乔普拉 (Rohit Chopra) 对非法收回汽车、取消抵押品赎回权和银行透支费用的严厉打击，使他成为消费者群体心目中的英雄和放贷者的敌人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Advent 考虑以 50 亿欧元出售仿制药制造商 Zentiva</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/advent-said-to-mull-5-billion-sale-of-generic-drugmaker-zentiva</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，收购公司 Advent International 正在考虑出售仿制药制造商 Zentiva，这笔交易对赛诺菲前子公司的估值可能达到约 50 亿欧元（54 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/advent-said-to-mull-5-billion-sale-of-generic-drugmaker-zentiva</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选后市场涨跌互现，油价难以找到方向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价稳定在每桶 72 美元附近，与昨日相比变化不大，交易员对唐纳德·特朗普当选可能对市场产生的影响感到矛盾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:27:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
